{"tha-ap252:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap252:0.2":"Tuvaradayakavagga ","tha-ap252:0.3":"10 Uddalakadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap252:1.1":"“Kakudho nama namena, ","tha-ap252:1.2":"sayambhu aparajito; ","tha-ap252:1.3":"Pavana nikkhamitvana, ","tha-ap252:1.4":"anuppatto mahanadim. ","tha-ap252:2.1":"Uddalakam gahetvana, ","tha-ap252:2.2":"sayambhussa adasaham; ","tha-ap252:2.3":"Samyatassujubhutassa, ","tha-ap252:2.4":"pasannamanaso aham. ","tha-ap252:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap252:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap252:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap252:3.4":"pupphadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap252:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap252:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap252:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap252:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma uddalakadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap252:6.1":"Uddalakadayakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap252:7.1":"Tuvaradayakavaggo pancavisatimo. ","tha-ap252:8.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap252:9.1":"Tuvaranaganalina, ","tha-ap252:9.2":"viravi kutidhupako; ","tha-ap252:9.3":"Patto dhatusattaliyo, ","tha-ap252:9.4":"bimbi uddalakena ca; ","tha-ap252:9.5":"Sattatimsati gathayo, ","tha-ap252:9.6":"ganitayo vibhavibhi. "}